            "id": 6007262,
            "title": "被關稅拖累的企業看過來！財部退還溢付稅額最高可退30萬元 4大重點一次看",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>財政部為協助受美國關稅政策影響發生營運困難之營業人，今 (4) 日發布，凡因受美國關稅政策影響，致營業收入減少者，得申請退還營業稅溢付稅額，累計退還限額為 30 萬元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007262%2Fl%2Fe82bacfe6445892c9a4668b31d04e026.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">被關稅拖累的企業看過來！財部退還溢付稅額最高可退30萬元 4大重點一次看。（鉅亨網資料照）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>資誠聯合會計師事務所稅務法律服務會計師林巨峯整理 4 大重點：</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1. 適用期間：美國評估及實施關稅政策影響期間；</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2. 適用對象：營業稅稅籍狀況為營業中之營業人；</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>3. 適用條件：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(1) 經主管機關因應美國關稅政策提供紓困、 補貼、補償、振興、支持或協助等相關措施；</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(2) 其他因受美國關稅政策影響，致營業收入減少。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>4. 營業人符合上述情形之一者，得申請退還營業稅溢付稅額，累計退還限額為 30 萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>林巨峯說明，過去 COVID-19 疫情期間，營業人留抵稅額可免專案報財政部核定退還，該次適用要件之一為營業收入減少達 15％。此次留抵稅額提前退稅之適用要件，同樣亦有營業收入減少，但並未設有一定百分比的限制，預料將會有更多營業人符合退稅資格。提醒營業人可於規定期間內檢具申請書及證明文件向所在地國稅局提出，國稅局將會從簡、從速辦理。另，如果有以營業稅留抵稅額作為補徵稅額或罰鍰擔保者，該部分不得申請退還。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6007262",
